{"tid":2085980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度禁用微信 指威脅國家安全及主權","createTime":"2020-06-30T06:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:32:06.000Z","uid":227801,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"864021bfee21dea2085921284b40437b98209b4a","tid":2085980,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=396177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396177&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=af0dbbca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396177&h=d9d665f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=396177</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】印度宣布禁用59個與中國有關的手機應用程式，指這些程式威脅印度的安全及主權。<br />\n<br />\n受影響的手機程式包括微信及TikTok，印度科技部指，收到投訴指有程式在未經用戶批准下，竊取及傳送用戶資料到印度以外的伺服器，對印度的國家安全及主權構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n根據當局命令，Google及蘋果需要在印度的手機應用程式商店移除有關程式。<br />\n<br />\n印度與中國軍隊早前在拉達克特區發生衝突，造成20名印度士兵死亡，令印度的反華情緒上升。"},{"pid":"5be19de0fa288b9870015520e737fb4d17f0c97a","tid":2085980,"uid":335303,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"去邊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案係!! 維園見(7月1)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為立國安法唔去維園啫係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n維園發音就係 喂完  喂完  未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係完未喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而香港人玩完未呀 係未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!7月1維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},{"pid":"a7bc78