183086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"全世界都一齊bam we7<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0382b83215e65b7b5ac52e6791773493cd9c4f43","tid":2085980,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:39:13.000Z","msg":"仲可以用apk安裝"},{"pid":"76974accee30b58f994cf5571a33399a63f6de98","tid":2085980,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5be19de0fa288b9870015520e737fb4d17f0c97a","tid":2085980,"uid":335303,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"去邊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案係!! 維園見(7月1)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為立國安法唔去維園啫係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n維園發音就係 喂完  喂完  未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係完未喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而香港人玩完未呀 係未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!7月1維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=c2be9c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"bf9c5446b481ce501fc1315b5c1204c0e2039b10","tid":2085980,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"做中國生意嘅人慘"},{"pid":"8a29a45825c6d51754cdef92d45a813f40979630","tid":2085980,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b58c2db72a40105a7c98d4f5e3b630f51cebe54","tid":2085980,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"估唔到印度先係最有guts<br />\n<br />\n美國搞左咁耐都仲未有實質抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec3217326cc613417887143c7a981b89cea3a02","tid":2085980,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e